thread.title: Steven

author: Steven
title: Steven
text: I was searching for a particular badminton racket and this site came up on my Google search, which seems a little odd as the site is mainly for gaming. The racket price was much lower here and I was a little suspicious, but they (I bought two) arrived a few days later and are excellent rackets. I've just checked the site again and the price has now doubled so I got a real bargain at the time.
